  "texts": [
    "It combines the results of classifiers like CRF, SVM and Maximum Entropy (ME), with a majority voting method in order to recognize entities in Bengali.",
    "In total, the training set is around 150-thousand-word forms.",
    "Each word form has been manually annotated with tags like person name, location name and organization name.",
    "Lexical context patterns, generated from an unlabeled corpus of 3-million-word forms were used to improve the performance of the classifiers and the recall, precision and f-score for this system are 87.11%, 83.61% and 85.32 respectively.",
    "Compared to the best performing SVM based system, this system has an increased f-score of 4.66%."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}